** CMD
CLRPFM QTEMP/ALCWP40
** ERR
DATE ERROR
FROM DATE > TODAY'S DATE.
NO DATA FOUND!
DATA OVER LIMIT! CHANGE SELECT CONDITION THEN TRY AGAIN.
PAGE# VALID WITH LOT#.





** LOC
GMSP           GEOMET
BZA            BZ-01 A-LINE
BZB            BZ-02 B-LINE
BZC            BZ-03 C-LINE
LG             LUBE GREEN
D3             AR8133
DR             SAFETY DRAW 711                                         711
LC             LUBE CLEAR
KW             WASHING
RE             RED
M1             RED
SB             SHOT BLAST
MAGNI          MAGNI
OUTS           OUTSOURCE
